These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae
1. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Game           | scrabble | mah-jongg |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | dubstep  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, lizard
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, spy
1. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | lizard   | goat      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | spy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
2 different pets are kept: cat, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, subway
1. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Pet   | mouse | cat    |
| Transport     | boat | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, zombie
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, thai
1. the thai is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | zombie |
| Nationality   | nigerian | thai |

