.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-10::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, disco
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, chess
1. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##5
2. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | country |
| Hobby     | chess   | photography    |

